  "description": "A long exposure night shot captures a vibrant fireworks display over a city skyline and a long bridge stretching across dark water. The fireworks explode in bursts of white, gold, and red, contrasting against the deep blue of the night sky. Below, the city is illuminated with numerous lights, creating a sparkling urban landscape. A prominent bridge with its cables and supports is visible in the foreground, with the faint outline of buildings and skyscrapers in the background. The water reflects some of the city lights and fireworks, adding to the overall luminous effect.",
